questionsAndAnswers.question: How does it work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: First, please contact me and send me your website URL. I will then give you explanations, answers and instructions about everything, so you can then proceed with an order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Does the app update automatically with the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! Every change you make on the website will be automatically visible in the app as well. The apps that I make display all the latest website content and changes that you make there.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What kind of app will I receive?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Please check my portfolio and contact me. Send me your website URL. Once we get in touch I will also send you live samples so that you know what kind of app to expect. I will use your website logo, 100% website color accuracy, font and style. Completely responsive and designed with care.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are there any monthly fees or similar?
My website is not in English. Is that a problem?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No problem whatsoever. I can make apps in any language.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What are push notifications and how do they work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You will get a control panel to install on your phone or computer from where you write a message, press send and all app users will be notified and receive the message. People's phones will vibrate and make a notification sound. It can be a special offer, an announcement, information, you name it.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you integrate my AdMob ads?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! For free! You will need to send me the App ID for each (Android and/or iOS) and also the Banner ID and/or Interstitial ID of each. Just make sure you don't have AdSense on the website because Google does not allow you to have both.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you work on custom projects? Do you make custom apps or work on other people's apps?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, I only convert websites into apps, and I only work on apps created by me.
